OL,3,CBoy, 14, pleads not guilty over
OL,4,Calleged plan to target two mosques
OL,6,FA 14 year-old boy allegedly drew up a
OL,7,Fplan motivated by "extreme right-wing
OL,8,Fideology" to attack worshippers at two
OL,9,Fmosques, a court has heard.
OL,11,FThe boy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,12,Freasons, was charged with an offence
OL,13,Flinked to "extreme right-wing
OL,14,Fterrorism" after police discovered an
OL,15,Falleged plan to target two mosques in
OL,16,FSutton, south London.
OL,18,FHe appeared at Westminster
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court in central London,
OL,20,Fsitting as a youth court, on Thursday,
OL,21,Fwhen he denied two charges.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@IO]uD@KOUvD@JO]
