OL,3,CBoy, 14, pleads not guilty over
OL,4,Calleged plan to target two mosques
OL,6,FThe boy, who was arrested in the south
OL,7,FLondon area, pleaded not guilty to a
OL,8,Fcharge of preparation of terrorist
OL,9,Facts on or before July 9, where it is
OL,10,Fsaid he identified targets, conducted
OL,11,Freconnaissance, identified a weapon
OL,12,Fand collected instructional material,
OL,13,Fin preparation for giving effect to an
OL,14,Fintention to conduct acts of
OL,15,Fterrorism, namely killing people at
OL,16,Fmosques in Sutton.
OL,18,FHe also pleaded not guilty to a charge
OL,19,Fof causing racially aggravated damage
OL,20,Fto property by allegedly damaging a
OL,21,Fcar window on or before June 20.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
